Privacy Policy - Blue Light Filter
Last Updated: 21.12.2022
Introduction
Welcome to “Blue Light Filter,” an iOS application designed to reduce blue light emitted by your device to protect your eyes and improve your sleep quality. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your information.
Contact Information:
For any privacy-related inquiries or concerns, please contact us at:
– Email: support@riviacorp.com
– Address:
